'''''Theologie und Glaube''''' is a German academic journal, published since 1909 by the Department of Theology of the [[University of Paderborn]]. {{As of|2015}}, the journal's editors are Herbert Haslinger, [[:de:Maria Neubrand]], and [[:de:Günter Wilhelms]].
